---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Classmates">
  <header class="reveal max-w-3xl">
    <span class="section-kicker">Mustangs of '06</span>
    <h1 class="mt-2 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-brand-900 sm:text-5xl">Classmates</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-brand-700">
      We don't try to duplicate what already exists — the Facebook group and the official
      alumni site are still the best places to find old classmates and keep up.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="reveal mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-5">
    <Card icon="👥" title="Class Facebook Group">
      <p>The most active place to reconnect, share photos, and see who's coming.</p>
      <a
        href="https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1G2ZxKc1GP/?mibextid=wwXIfr"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group/cta mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-cream-50 shadow-[0_2px_0_rgba(13,11,10,0.04),0_8px_18px_-6px_rgba(242,105,1,0.5)] transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-brand-600 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Open Facebook group
        <span class="text-cream-50/70 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/cta:translate-x-0.5" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </Card>
    <Card icon="🎓" title="Official Clio High alumni site">
      <p>Class roster, class history, and links to other reunion years.</p>
      <a
        href="https://cliohighschool.net/class-of-2006.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group/cta mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-brand-300 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-700 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-50 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        cliohighschool.net
        <span class="text-brand-500 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/cta:translate-x-0.5" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </Card>
  </section>

  <section class="reveal mt-16 sm:mt-20">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-cream-300 bg-white/80 p-8 shadow-soft sm:p-12">
      <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-accent-400 via-accent-300 to-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative">
        <span class="section-kicker">Round 'em up</span>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-heading text-2xl font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-brand-900 sm:text-3xl">Help us find everyone.</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-brand-700">
          Lost touch with a classmate? Know somebody who isn't in the Facebook group?
          <a href="/contact" class="font-semibold text-brand-900 underline decoration-accent-400 decoration-2 underline-offset-4">Send us their name</a>
          and we'll do our best to track them down before the reunion.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
